{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/gakuen-babysitters-pentingnya-penitipan-anak-di-tempat-kerja/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Gakuen Babysitters: Pentingnya Penitipan Anak di Tempat Kerja","content":"<p>Ada satu <em>anime</em> menarik bertema <em>slice of life</em>Â yang sedang tayang di awal tahun ini: Gakuen Babysitters. Anime Gakuen Babysitters ini tayang sebanyak 12 episode dan saat ini sudah memasuki episode keempat.</p>\n<p>Saya paling senang dengan <em>anime-anime</em> singkat yang hanya berjalan sepanjang 12 episode seperti ini, karena tidak memerlukan usaha keras untuk up to date dengan setiap episodenya. Biasanya untuk <em>anime</em> dengan episode panjang (apalagi jika episode <em>filler-</em>nya banyak), saya lebih memilih untuk membaca <em>manga</em>nya saja. Saya juga tidak bisa membayangkan menjadi wibu akut. Hehehe.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_42663\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-42663\" data-attachment-id=\"42663\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/gakuen-babysitters-pentingnya-penitipan-anak-di-tempat-kerja/attachment/01-gakuen-babysitters/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/01-gakuen-babysitters.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01 gakuen babysitters\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/01-gakuen-babysitters-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/01-gakuen-babysitters.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42663\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/01-gakuen-babysitters.jpg\" alt=\"01 gakuen babysitters\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/01-gakuen-babysitters.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/01-gakuen-babysitters-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-42663\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Rugrats versi anime? (Sumber: Lost in Anime)</p></div></p>\n<p>Hal lain yang membuat saya senang dengan anime ini: anak kecil! <em>Kyaaa!</em> <em>Anyway,</em> Gakuen Babysitters awalnya adalah serial <em>manga</em> yang diciptakan Hari Tokeino dan diterbitkan secara bertahap di majalah <em>shoujo</em> Hakusensha, sebelum akhirnya diadaptasi menjadi <em>anime</em> di awal Januari ini.</p>\n<p><em>Anime</em> ini bercerita tentang sebuah klub <em>babysitter</em> di akademi Morinomiya yang diperuntukkan kepada para guru perempuan yang mengajar di akademi tersebut. Uniknya, para pengasuh yang berada di klub <em>babysitter</em> itu adalah para laki-laki. <em>Anime</em> ini mengingatkan saya dengan Return of Superman, acara televisi Korea yang menampilkan para ayah yang mengasuh anaknya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_42664\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-42664\" data-attachment-id=\"42664\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/gakuen-babysitters-pentingnya-penitipan-anak-di-tempat-kerja/attachment/02-tablo/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/02-tablo.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02 tablo\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/02-tablo-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/02-tablo.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42664\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/02-tablo.jpg\" alt=\"02 tablo\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/02-tablo.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/02-tablo-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-42664\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Haru dan Tablo di Return of Superman (Sumber: KBS World)</p></div></p>\n<p>Tak perlu berlama-lama, yuk kita kenalan dengan anak-anak unyu nan lucu di anime ini!</p>\n<h1>Kotaro Kashima</h1>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_42665\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-42665\" data-attachment-id=\"42665\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/gakuen-babysitters-pentingnya-penitipan-anak-di-tempat-kerja/attachment/03-kotaro/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/03-kotaro.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03 kotaro\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/03-kotaro-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/03-kotaro.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42665\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/03-kotaro.jpg\" alt=\"03 kotaro\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/03-kotaro.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/03-kotaro-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-42665\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kotaro Kashima (Sumber: Zerochan)</p></div></p>\n<p>Kotaro merupakan adik Ryuichi Kashima, salah satu pengasuh di klub <em>babysitter</em> ini. Karakternya kalem dan datar, seolah-olah tanpa ekspresi. Tapi, sebenarnya dia menyimpan emosi yang besar kepada kakaknya, dan akan merasa sangat sedih jika terpisah dari sang kakak. Salah satu momen yang paling saya suka adalah ketika Kotaro kesusahan memeras lemon saat membuat minuman agar kakaknya sembuh dari sakit pilek. <em>Uuh!</em></p>\n<h1>Taka Kamitani</h1>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_42666\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-42666\" data-attachment-id=\"42666\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/gakuen-babysitters-pentingnya-penitipan-anak-di-tempat-kerja/attachment/04-taka/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/04-taka.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04 taka\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/04-taka-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/04-taka.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42666\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/04-taka.jpg\" alt=\"04 taka\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/04-taka.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/04-taka-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-42666\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Taka Kamitani (sumber: Zerochan)</p></div></p>\n<p>Taka merupakan adik Hayato Kamitani, salah satu anggota klub <em>baseball</em> di akademi yang nantinya akan ikut bergabung dalam klub <em>babysitter</em>. Berbeda dengan hubungan Kotaro dan kakaknya yang manis, Taka sering kali bertengkar dengan kakaknya, apalagi Hayato tak jarang memarahinya dengan kasar. Taka merupakan karakter yang banyak bicara dan banyak tingkah, tapi bukannya menjengkelkan. Justru karakternya itu membuatnya semakin unyu!</p>\n<h1>Kirin Kumatsuka</h1>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_42669\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-42669\" data-attachment-id=\"42669\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/gakuen-babysitters-pentingnya-penitipan-anak-di-tempat-kerja/attachment/05-kirin/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/05-kirin.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05 kirin\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/05-kirin-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/05-kirin.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42669\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/05-kirin.jpg\" alt=\"05 kirin\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/05-kirin.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/05-kirin-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-42669\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kirin Kumatsuka (sumber: Zerochan)</p></div></p>\n<p>Kirin merupakan satu-satunya anak perempuan yang diasuh dalam klub <em>babysitter,</em> selain Midori yang masih bayi. Kirin merupakan anak yang ceria dan sering membanggakan kepang rambut yang dibuat oleh ibunya. Sosok Kirin membuat saya ingat kepada Haru dalam Return of Superman.</p>\n<h1>Midori Sawatori</h1>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_42684\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-42684\" data-attachment-id=\"42684\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/gakuen-babysitters-pentingnya-penitipan-anak-di-tempat-kerja/attachment/06-midori/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/06-midori.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"06 midori\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/06-midori-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/06-midori.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42684\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/06-midori.jpg\" alt=\"06 midori\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/06-midori.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/06-midori-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-42684\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Midori Sawatori (sumber: Zerochan)</p></div></p>\n<p>Satu-satunya anak yang masih berusia bayi dan dibawa oleh Usaida kemana-mana. Ia belum bisa banyak berbicara, namun sering ikut menimbrung dengan kata-kata yang ia ucapkan secara tidak jelas tapi tentu saja, manis.</p>\n<h1>Takuma &amp; Kazuma Mamizuka</h1>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_42691\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-42691\" data-attachment-id=\"42691\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/gakuen-babysitters-pentingnya-penitipan-anak-di-tempat-kerja/attachment/07-takuma/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/07-takuma.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"07 takuma\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/07-takuma-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/07-takuma.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42691\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/07-takuma.jpg\" alt=\"07 takuma\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/07-takuma.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/07-takuma-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-42691\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Anak pertama, Takuma (Sumber: Pinterest)</p></div></p>\n<p>Kazuma dan Takuma merupakan saudara kembar dengan karakter yang bertolak belakang. Takuma, sang kakak, mempunyai karakter yang lebih ceria. Sedangkan Kazuma, adiknya, seringkali memperlihatkan wajah yang seolah-olah akan menangis. Kembar ini mengingatkan saya kepada <em>The Triplet </em>dalam Return of Superman.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_42692\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-42692\" data-attachment-id=\"42692\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/gakuen-babysitters-pentingnya-penitipan-anak-di-tempat-kerja/attachment/08-kazuma/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/08-kazuma.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"08 kazuma\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/08-kazuma-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/08-kazuma.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42692\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/08-kazuma.jpg\" alt=\"08 kazuma\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/08-kazuma.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/08-kazuma-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-42692\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Anak kedua, Kazuma (Sumber: Pinterest)</p></div></p>\n<p>Mereka mempunyai ayah yang bekerja sebagai seorang aktor yang jarang mereka temui, sehingga ayahnya merasa bahwa mereka tidak mengenalinya. Hal itu berujung pada sebuah adegan mengharukan ketika Kazuma dan Takuma mendatangi ayah mereka yang dikerubungi fans dan memanggilnya âPapa!â Meski demikian, menurut saya adegan Kotaru memeras lemon untuk kakaknya masih jauh lebih mengharukan. Hehehe.</p>\n<h1>Pentingnya Tempat Penitipan Anak di Tempat Kerja</h1>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_42693\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-42693\" data-attachment-id=\"42693\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/gakuen-babysitters-pentingnya-penitipan-anak-di-tempat-kerja/attachment/09-guru/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/09-guru.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"09 guru\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/09-guru-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/09-guru.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42693\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/09-guru.jpg\" alt=\"09 guru\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/09-guru.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/09-guru-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-42693\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Beberapa guru perempuan di akademi Morinomiya yang menitipkan anaknya di klub babysitter. (sumber: Lost in Anime)</p></div></p>\n<p>Sejak awal menonton Gakuen Babysitters, melihat bagaimana <em>anime</em> ini menceritakan bahwa klub <em>babysitter</em> itu diperuntukkan untuk para guru perempuan yang bekerja di akademi Mironimiya, saya langsung teringat beberapa guru di sekolah saya dulu. Setiap saat setelah melahirkan anak, mereka sangat kerepotan dengan tugas mengurus anak dan mengajar, sehingga kadang mereka harus menitipkan anaknya kepada guru perempuan lain yang sedang tidak bertugas mengajar.</p>\n<p><em>Merepotkan sekali, </em>batin saya kala itu. Saya pun teringat akan hal lain; sesuatu yang diucapkan oleh Dian Sastrowardoyo dalam sebuah wawancara di film Kartini: pentingnya tempat penitipan anak di tempat kerja di Indonesia.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_42694\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-42694\" data-attachment-id=\"42694\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/gakuen-babysitters-pentingnya-penitipan-anak-di-tempat-kerja/attachment/09-penitipan/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/09-penitipan.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"10 penitipan\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/09-penitipan-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/09-penitipan.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42694\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/09-penitipan.jpg\" alt=\"10 penitipan\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/09-penitipan.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/09-penitipan-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-42694\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sebuah tempat penitipan anak di Pekanbaru. (Sumber: Youtube)</p></div></p>\n<p>Kementerian Pemberdayaan Perempuan dan Perlindungan Anak sendiri, pada tahun 2015 pernah mengeluarkan Peraturan Menteri yang mewajibkan seluruh instansi pemerintah dan swasta menyediakan tempat penitipan anak dan Ruang khusus ASI. Namun, entah isu ini ditanggapi secara serius atau tidak sampai hari ini. Tempat penitipan anak di tempat kerja membuat orangtua lebih efisien dalam mengawasi anaknya, apalagi jika anak itu masih membutuhkan ASI.</p>\n<p>Jepang sendiri, berama negara lain seperti Turki dan Belanda, mulai mewajibkan perusahaan untuk menyediakan tempat penitipan anak. Untuk tempat kerja lain, saya sendiri belum mendapatkan informasinya. Meski demikian, hal ini bukan sekedar isu sepele. <strong>Kesetaraan <em>gender</em> </strong>dan <strong>tuntutan ekonomi</strong> telah membawa perempuan yang dulunya hanya ibu rumah tangga menjadi salah satu tenaga penggerak industri. Maka demikian, isu ini harus dibahas secara serius. Bukan begitu, bro sis?</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"82614698-843e-5d9a-96e0-364c7b951975"}}}